Agile is a methodology to deploy your application in a small chuncks in a sprint manner

Early, we used to deploy using waterfall model 
    - In waterfall model we acquire everythng in one go and implement in one go
    - so it takes lot of time to reach the customers


Jira tool is a project management tool, it is sued to track the progress of a project in sprint 
    - it have dashboard
confluence is a knowledge sharing platform
servicenow is a incident or change management tool
